==English==
===Etymology===
from Latin ''serpere'' to creep

===Noun===
'''serpent'''
# A [[snake]].
# {{musici}} A [[musical]] [[instrument]] in the [[brass]] family, whose shape is suggestive of a snake ([[w:Serpent (instrument)|Wikipedia article]]).

====Related terms====
*[[serpentine]]

